      <title>1843 Nov. 15, Franklin, Tennessee [to] Hester Ann Fergusson, Carthage, Tennessee / A[dam] Fergusson</title>
   </titleInfo>
   <abstract>This is a letter from Adam Fergusson to his wife Hester Ann, dated November 15, 1843. Fergusson is on his way to Nashville and is writing to update Hester on his progress. He writes of some of the people he has encountered so far.</abstract>
